    <section class="section narrative-section" id="system">
      <div class="narrative-copy">
        <div class="eyebrow">WHAT CLIPENCY IS</div>
        <h2>A campaign distribution system for brands that want movement, proof and measurable execution.</h2>
        <p>
          Most campaigns lose momentum between planning and distribution. Briefs sit in documents, creators are coordinated through scattered messages, proof gets lost, and performance becomes difficult to verify. Clipency turns that chaos into a controlled workflow.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="narrative-stack">
        <article>
          <span>01</span>
          <strong>Campaigns become structured</strong>
          <p>Every campaign can carry its goal, platform, payout logic, submission requirements and status.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <span>02</span>
          <strong>Creators become operators</strong>
          <p>Clippers discover campaigns, publish content, submit proof links and track their progress.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <span>03</span>
          <strong>Teams get one control layer</strong>
          <p>Submissions, approvals, insights and payouts can live in one system instead of endless chat threads.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

